<Page
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
  xmlns:i="http://schemas.microsoft.com/xaml/behaviors"
  xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
  xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
  xmlns:local="clr-namespace:SeapowerUI"
  mc:Ignorable="d"
  d:DesignWidth="1920"
  d:DesignHeight="1080"
  Width="{Binding RelativeSource={RelativeSource Mode=FindAncestor, AncestorType={x:Type ContentControl}}, Path=ActualWidth, FallbackValue=700}"
  Height="{Binding RelativeSource={RelativeSource Mode=FindAncestor, AncestorType={x:Type ContentControl}}, Path=ActualHeight, FallbackValue=400}"
  Padding="5,5,5,5">
	<ScrollViewer>
	<StackPanel Orientation="Vertical">
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="15" FontFamily="Roboto" FontSize="12">
<Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="視角控制" FontSize="16"/>
<LineBreak/>
<LineBreak/>
我們從視角控制開始。在遊戲中任何未被視窗覆蓋的位置按住左鍵即可圍繞船艦旋轉視角。你可以按<Run Text="{Binding InputBindingDict[HideHUD], Source={StaticResource InputHandlerInterface}}"/>隱藏和恢復使用者介面。
<LineBreak/>
<LineBreak/>
現在嘗試旋轉視角，當然也可以探索水下！
		</TextBlock>	

        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="0" HorizontalAlignment="Center">
			<Button Width="100" Height="50" Margin="0,0,15,0" FontSize="16" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Content="上一頁" Command="{Binding OpenFileCommand}" CommandParameter="missions/Tutorials/Officer_Training_1_briefing/t01_window_2_cn.xml"/>
			<Button Width="100" Height="50" Margin="0" FontSize="16" VerticalAlignment="Bottom" Content="下一頁" Command="{Binding OpenFileCommand}" CommandParameter="missions/Tutorials/Officer_Training_1_briefing/t01_window_4_cn.xml"/>	
		</StackPanel>
	</StackPanel>
	</ScrollViewer>
</Page>